						<p><hi rend="bold">Tirumalai Nāyakkarayyaṉ. Śaka 1562: A.D. 1641.</hi></p>						

						<p>(<hi rend="italic">Vishu (Vrusha), Kārttikai</hi>, Wednesday (irregular) = A.D. 1641.).</p>						

						<p>Much damaged. Seems to record a gift of the village Vēmbaṭṭi to Iḷaiyanayiṉār Kumārasuvāmi of Tirupparaṅkuṉṟam, for the merit of the Madurai Nāyaka king, Tirumalai Nāyakkarayyaṉ.</p>						

